343
00:25:06,638 --> 00:25:08,073
- Let's go, move.

344
00:25:09,007 --> 00:25:12,177
(exotic action music)

345
00:25:45,844 --> 00:25:49,514
All right, other side of that ridge is Cambodia.

346
00:25:49,514 --> 00:25:52,417
Once we cross that border, we no longer exist.

347
00:25:52,417 --> 00:25:54,052
- What happens if we get caught?

348
00:25:54,052 --> 00:25:57,022
- Don't expect any help from the actual MAC, sonny boy.

349
00:25:57,022 --> 00:25:59,557
- Yeah, in other words, don't fuck up.

350
00:26:01,927 --> 00:26:02,761
- Let's move.

351
00:26:08,533 --> 00:26:11,202
- Sir, Captain Thuy is here to see you.

352
00:26:11,202 --> 00:26:12,037
- Send him in.

353
00:26:19,444 --> 00:26:20,412
- Colonel.

354
00:26:20,412 --> 00:26:21,680
- What is it, Thuy?

355
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,615
- I am convinced that Major Vo was murdered.

356
00:26:24,816 --> 00:26:26,518
- [Horace] Do you think the Cong did it?

357
00:26:26,518 --> 00:26:27,786
- [Tan] No, sir, I don't.

358
00:26:29,054 --> 00:26:30,288
- Who then?

359
00:26:30,288 --> 00:26:32,057
- Apparently someone on the base, sir.

360
00:26:33,058 --> 00:26:33,892
- An American?

361
00:26:35,460 --> 00:26:38,363
That's a very interesting theory, Captain Thuy.

362
00:26:38,363 --> 00:26:41,232
What are your analyses?

363
00:26:41,232 --> 00:26:44,636
- We recovered three bullets from the body, sir.

364
00:26:44,636 --> 00:26:46,271
They were all US-issued.

365
00:26:46,271 --> 00:26:48,139
- Well, I don't think that proves anything.

366
00:26:48,139 --> 00:26:52,043
We all know the VC have plenty of US-made firearms.

367
00:26:52,043 --> 00:26:56,047
- I beg the colonel's pardon, but being Major Vo's adjutant,

368
00:26:56,047 --> 00:26:59,050
I am well aware of the fact that for months now

369
00:26:59,050 --> 00:27:02,354
you and your men have been persecuting him relentlessly.

370
00:27:03,688 --> 00:27:06,391
- Just what are you proposing?

371
00:27:06,391 --> 00:27:08,059
- I'd like to take ballistics of every sidearm

372
00:27:08,059 --> 00:27:10,195
of every man in this CP, sir.

373
00:27:10,195 --> 00:27:13,298
- No way, Captain Thuy, no fucking way.

374
00:27:14,866 --> 00:27:16,401
- In that case, colonel, if you don't mind,

375
00:27:16,401 --> 00:27:18,937
I'll take my request to MACV.

376
00:27:18,937 --> 00:27:21,539
- Go ahead, be my guest.

377
00:27:21,539 --> 00:27:23,541
They'll laugh in your little brown face.

378
00:27:23,541 --> 00:27:27,612
- You know, Thuy, VC activity in Tay Ninh has dropped off

379
00:27:27,612 --> 00:27:30,949
85% since Major Vo's untimely demise.

380
00:27:30,949 --> 00:27:33,718
Everybody knew Vo was a double agent.

381
00:27:33,718 --> 00:27:35,754
The VC drained him of all the information they had

382
00:27:35,754 --> 00:27:37,422
and finished him off, that's all.

383
00:27:37,422 --> 00:27:39,524
- That sort of an allegation could never stand up

384
00:27:39,524 --> 00:27:41,826
in an American court of law, you know that, sir.

385
00:27:41,826 --> 00:27:44,562
And even if he was guilty of what you said he did,

386
00:27:44,562 --> 00:27:46,564
he still deserved due process.

387
00:27:46,564 --> 00:27:47,966
Right now it all seems nothing

388
00:27:47,966 --> 00:27:50,368
but an execution doesn't it, colonel?

389
00:27:50,368 --> 00:27:54,172
- You listen to me, chief of police

390
00:27:54,172 --> 00:27:56,541
pops a VC in the head right in the streets

391
00:27:56,541 --> 00:27:58,677
of Saigon in front of God, the TV cameras,

392
00:27:58,677 --> 00:28:00,812
and everybody, and you come complaining to me?

393
00:28:02,013 --> 00:28:06,084
I suggest you drop this, that is my best advice.

394
00:28:06,084 --> 00:28:07,118
- Yes, sir.

395
00:28:18,463 --> 00:28:20,131
- What do you think?

396
00:28:20,131 --> 00:28:21,599
- God, he's bluffing.

397
00:28:21,599 --> 00:28:24,335
Anyway, they'd never take his word over mine.

