447
00:35:01,532 --> 00:35:02,467
Bloomquist.

448
00:35:03,634 --> 00:35:05,136
Bloomquist, he was right beside me.

449
00:35:05,136 --> 00:35:07,572
(gunfire and screaming)

450
00:35:07,572 --> 00:35:08,840
