455
00:35:38,803 --> 00:35:41,138
(screaming)

456
00:35:58,623 --> 00:36:00,424
- We gotta pull this down, Troop.

457
00:36:00,424 --> 00:36:02,026
We can't let 'em get away with this.

458
00:36:02,026 --> 00:36:02,860
- Hold on.

459
