- Hey, poppy, look what I found over there.

824
01:13:54,530 --> 01:13:58,300
- Why don't we hear what she has to say about that.

825
01:13:58,300 --> 01:13:59,802
- It's my brother's.

826
01:13:59,802 --> 01:14:03,138
He keeps in touch with the South, we have a common enemy.

827
01:14:03,138 --> 01:14:04,473
(laughing)

828
01:14:04,473 --> 01:14:05,774
- The man's dead, Wiggins.

829
