The enemy's all around us.

846
01:15:15,110 --> 01:15:17,412
Look at 'em, they got no feelings.

847
01:15:20,949 --> 01:15:22,351
- They hurt just like we do.

848
01:15:23,952 --> 01:15:26,755
- Shut the fuck up, Holland.

849
01:15:26,755 --> 01:15:28,957
Act like you got a pair.

850
01:15:28,957 --> 01:15:30,792
These people aren't even human,

851
01:15:30,792 --> 01:15:33,395
they're just a bunch of lying asshole motherfuckers.

852
01:15:35,364 --> 01:15:37,499
- You've lost it, haven't you?

853
01:15:37,499 --> 01:15:39,401
You've really fucking lost it.

854
01:15:39,401 --> 01:15:40,569
- Shut him up.

855
01:15:42,571 --> 01:15:44,139
Don't sweat it, son,

856
01:15:45,307 --> 01:15:48,010
