857
01:15:49,111 --> 01:15:52,981
It'll be over before you know it.

858
01:15:52,981 --> 01:15:53,949
Year of the Monkey.

859
01:15:57,119 --> 01:16:00,422
(rapid gunfire)

860
01:16:00,422 --> 01:16:01,557
- Wiggins, no!

861
01:16:04,293 --> 01:16:06,762
- I'm doing what they wanted me to do.

862
01:16:06,762 --> 01:16:09,865
